## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **fruquintinib Fruzaqla 2023** = first FDA selective VEGFR1/2/3 mCRC (FRESCO-2). regorafenib multi-kinase 후 selective VEGFR — refractory mCRC paradigm. quantum-VQE 의 VEGFR1/2/3 selectivity profiling fit.
2. **sotorasib + adagrasib 2024 mCRC + EGFR combo** = KRAS G12C mCRC 임상 진입 (CodeBreaK 300 + KRYSTAL-1). KRAS GTP-loaded vs GDP-loaded 다른 결합 mode + EGFR feedback resistance 가 mCRC 에서 lung 보다 더 prominent. quantum-VQE 의 KRAS allosteric pocket leverage.
3. **encorafenib + cetuximab 2020 (BEACON CRC)** = first FDA BRAF V600E mCRC — BRAF mono 가 melanoma 와 다르게 mCRC 에서 EGFR feedback 으로 fail. 다중-targeted resistance paradigm. quantum-VQE 의 BRAF V600E + EGFR Fab 결합 dual.
4. **dostarlimab Jemperli 2024 신생 MMR-d rectal CR without surgery (Cercek 2022 NEJM)** = MMR-d rectal 100% complete response 임상 paradigm shift. surgery + adjuvant chemo 면제. 임상 의의 폭발적.
5. **pembrolizumab 2017 first tissue-agnostic MSI-H/dMMR + 2020 KEYNOTE-177 1L mCRC** = MSI-H mCRC 1L IO. 임상 paradigm shift — chemo 가 아니라 IO 1L MSI-H. quantum-VQE 의 PD-1/PD-L1 interface fit.
6. **larotrectinib 2018 + entrectinib 2019 NTRK fusion tissue-agnostic** = NTRK fusion mCRC 희귀 (<1%) 이지만 tissue-agnostic 첫 FDA. quantum-VQE 의 NTRK fusion-specific kinase pocket leverage.
7. **HER2-amplified mCRC + T-DXd DESTINY-CRC-01** = HER2-amplified mCRC 3-5% — T-DXd ADC 가 chemo 후 next mechanism. tucatinib + trastuzumab MOUNTAINEER. cross-adc + cross-cancer.
8. **bevacizumab 2004 first FDA VEGF mAb mCRC** = VEGF anti-angiogenic 이 mCRC 에서 first 임상 적용 — 20+ year backbone. ramucirumab + ziv-aflibercept + regorafenib + fruquintinib 가 sequential VEGF axis evolution.
9. **Lynch syndrome 1차예방 aspirin + colonoscopy** = Lynch 가족성 5-10% CRC — aspirin chemoprevention + colonoscopy 1차예방. cross-inherited_adult + cross-preventive. 임상 paradigm — disease-modifying 가 아니라 prevention.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, mCRC + rectal + Lynch 임상 의미 한정.

